Diagram PNGs: committed here and loaded on the storefront via GitHub raw
  https://raw.githubusercontent.com/emcc10/mccabe-site/main/vspfiles/sectional-diagrams/{Style}-SC-{code}.png
  (see mtl-sectional-renderer.js — DEFAULT_MTL_SECTIONAL_DIAGRAM_BASE / window.MTL_SECTIONAL_DIAGRAM_BASE).

Legacy Volusion path /v/vspfiles/sectional-diagrams/… still works if you override the base back to your CDN.

Regenerate from Palliser Product Summary PDFs (auto crop, 300 DPI default):
  tools/sectional-diagrams/export_diagrams.ps1
or:  python tools/sectional-diagrams/export_sectional_diagrams.py --publish

When adding a NEW style: add rows in vspfiles/js/sectional-configs.js + one palliser block in tools/sectional-diagrams/catalog.json, run export, commit the new PNGs here, push to main.
